title: Sporting Rifle - March 2016
description:
English | 124 pages | PDF | 44.6 Mb

The UK's best live quarry rifle shooting magazine published 4-weekly, Sporting Rifle covers everything you need to know about deer stalking, vermin control, foxing and more. Full of tips and techniques, kit reviews, features and up-to-date news, Sporting Rifle is hugely popular with stalkers, gamekeepers, big game hunters and airgunners alike
